---
description: Governance constraints for Agile artifacts in docs/specs/agile-artifacts.
globs:
  - docs/specs/agile-artifacts/**/*.md
alwaysApply: true
---

- Canonical artifacts belong in `docs/specs/agile-artifacts/02-phase-artifacts`.
- Delivery deltas and evidence belong in `docs/specs/agile-artifacts/03-delivery-records`.
- Keep `INDEX.md` and `artifact-registry.md` synchronized when adding, moving, or archiving delivery records.
- Preserve lifecycle states (`Draft`, `In Review`, `Approved`, `Superseded`, `Archived`) consistently.
- Do not invent evidence, sign-off, or metrics values; explicitly mark missing information.
